  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/software-apps/\" rel=\"tag\">软件应用</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/vine-windows-phone-draft-mode/\"><img alt=\"Vine for Windows Phone\" src=\"http://hss-prod.hss.aol.com/hss/storage/adam/cd43dab847773278b938734990307dc8/vine-windows-phone.jpg\" /></a></div>\n\n<div><br />\n虽说 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/11/12/vine-for-windows-phone/\">Windows Phone 版的 Vine</a> 具备了许多其它平台版本的功能，但草稿模式并不是其中之一。每当你需要切换到别的程序时，六秒钟的苦功就会毁于一旦。而开发团队显然也看到了这个问题，并在最近的更新中添入了相应的功能，让使用者可以在方便的时候，继续编辑之前没有处理好的短片。不过遗憾的是，这个版本并没有给用户「<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/10/24/vine-now-lets-you-edit-and-work-on-multiple-posts-over-time/\">重来一次</a>」的机会，希望在不久的将来可以补上吧。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2013/12/18/vine-windows-phone-draft-mode/\">Engadget</a>、<span class=\"via\"><a href=\"http://www.phonearena.com/news/Vine-for-Windows-Phone-updated-with-draft-support_id50493?utm_source=feedburner&amp;utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_campaign=Feed%3A%20phonearena%2FySoL%20%28Phone%20Arena%20-%20Latest%20News%29\" target=\"_blank\">Phone Arena</a></span><br />\n引用来源：<span class=\"source\"><a href=\"http://www.windowsphone.com/en-us/store/app/vine/f9e6f07e-e47e-47f5-806d-55d4f79f2b60\" target=\"_blank\">Windows Phone Store</a></span></div><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/vine-windows-phone-draft-mode/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20791547/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/12/18/vine-windows-phone-draft-mode/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
